### From UI_WIREFRAMES.md
âœ… **Screens Defined:**
1. Design System (Colors, Typography, Components)
2. Onboarding Flow (4 screens)
3. Home Dashboard (Main hub)
4. Skin Analysis Camera (CV integration)
5. Routine Builder (Customization)
6. Routine Tracker (Daily progress)
7. Product Search (Browse catalog)
8. Product Detail (Info + reviews)
9. Community Forum (Posts + discussions)
10. User Profile (Settings + stats)

### From TECHNOLOGY_STACK.md
âœ… **Tech Requirements:**
- **Framework:** Flutter 3.22+
- **Language:** Dart 3.4+
- **State Management:** Provider + Riverpod
- **API:** HTTP 0.13 + Dio 5.4
- **Database:** Hive + SQLite
- **Authentication:** Firebase Auth
- **Storage:** Firebase Storage
- **Analytics:** Firebase Analytics
- **Image Processing:** Image 4.1 + OpenCV
- **Camera:** Camera 0.10
- **UI Components:** Material 3 + Cupertino

