## PART 3: CORE SCREENS (TO IMPLEMENT)

### Screen 1: Splash & Onboarding
- Animated splash screen (2 seconds)
- Welcome flow (4 screens)
- Profile setup form
- Preference selection
- **State Management:** Provider
- **Navigation:** Named routes

### Screen 2: Home Dashboard  
- AI recommendations (top 5)
- Daily routine reminder
- Progress card
- Quick access buttons
- Personalized feed
- **Data:** Firebase + Local cache
- **Updates:** Real-time

### Screen 3: Skin Analysis
- Camera integration
- Real-time image capture
- AI processing (local + cloud)
- Result display
- History timeline
- Photo comparison
- **Technologies:** Camera + OpenCV + TensorFlow
- **Performance:** <2s analysis

### Screen 4: Routine Manager
- Builder interface
- Product selection
- Schedule configuration
- Progress tracking
- Notifications
- **Features:** Drag-drop, calendar view
- **Storage:** SQLite + Hive

### Screen 5: Product Discovery
- Search & filter
- Recommendations
- Product details
- Reviews & ratings
- Save favorites
- **Data:** REST API
- **Caching:** Hive

### Screen 6: Community
- Forum threads
- Post creation
- Comments & replies
- User profiles
- Follow system
- **Real-time:** Firebase Realtime DB

### Screen 7: User Profile
- User stats
- Achievement badges
- Settings
- Account management
- Privacy controls

