## PART 5: CODE QUALITY STANDARDS

âœ… **Performance:**
- App startup: <1.5 seconds
- Screen transitions: <300ms
- API calls: <2 seconds
- Memory: <100MB average
- Frame rate: 60 FPS locked

âœ… **Code Quality:**
- Null safety: 100%
