## PART 6: IMPLEMENTATION SEQUENCE

**Phase 1 (Days 1-3):** Foundation
1. Project structure setup
2. Theme & design system
3. Navigation system
4. Error handling

**Phase 2 (Days 4-7):** Authentication
1. Auth service integration
2. Login/signup screens
3. Token management
4. Session handling

**Phase 3 (Days 8-14):** Core Features
1. Home dashboard
2. Skin analysis camera
3. Routine builder
4. Product search

**Phase 4 (Days 15-21):** Advanced Features
1. Community forum
2. Social sharing
3. Notifications
4. Analytics

**Phase 5 (Days 22-28):** Polish
1. Performance optimization
2. Testing
3. Bug fixes
4. Release build

